headline: They Rallied To Vote ‘No’ For Trump: This Is Why
abstract: Several Senate Republicans said that even if President Trump did everything impeachment managers said, he should not be removed.
lead_paragraph: The Senate voted on Friday nearly along party lines to block additional witnesses and evidence in President Trump’s impeachment trial, effectively accelerating the proceedings toward a final vote, which is expected to be held Wednesday.
keywords: Trump-Ukraine Whistle-blower Complaint and Impeachment Inquiry
